    <title>Women's Advancement contributor: Monica Mhoja</title>
    <description>Monica Mhoja is Tanzania program director at Landesa. She is also the founder of the Women’s Legal Aid Center and facilitated the establishment of 18 paralegal centers in 13 regions in Tanzania to provide legal aid services.She is a 2003 recipient of the American Bar Association’s International Human Rights Award for significant contribution to human rights, rule of law and access to justice.
</description>
