      <title>Branded as Witches, Stripped of Land: Tanzania’s Widows Need Support</title>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/womensadvancement/asset-and-property-rights/">Asset and Property Rights</category>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Apr 2018 10:50:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Monica Mhoja</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/womensadvancement/community/2018/04/12/branded-as-witches-stripped-of-land-tanzanias-widows-need-support</link>
